g.text: Starts the process of removing a courier.
Shows to the Administrator a list of pharmacies and asks him to choose the one he wants to remove a courier of.
Selects the Pharmacy he wants to remove a courier of.
Shows to the Administrator a list of couriers and asks him to choose the one he wants to remove.
Selects the courier he wants to remove.
Displays the data, asking him to confirm it.
Informs about the success of the operation.
